text: hananim-i heulg-eseo neohuileul changjohasa dasi jeong-aeg-eseo neohuileul jae changjo hasyeoss-eumyeo neohuileul ssang-eulo du syeossnola eotteohan yeoseongdo geubun-ui a sim-i eobs-ineun ingtaewa chulsan-eul hal sueobs-eumyeo eotteohan ingando saengmyeong-eul yeon janghageona danchughal su eobsnani i modeun geos-eun seongseo an-e issnola ileo han geos-eun sillo hananimkke swiun il-ila
